    title: "case 1 ",
    description:
      "Our team will get to know the processes in which you wish to automate. FVM will then be able to give recommendations on which tasks to automate to make your business more efficient.",
    icon: "bx:dice-1",
  },
  {
    title: "Solution Design",
    description:
      "FVM will design prototypes for the procedures agreed upon in the discovery stage. Once approved FVM will make final edits and dashboards.",
