      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-4xl font-semibold lg:tracking-tight xl:tracking-tighter">
        Slash Costs, Skyrocket Profits
      </h2>
    <p class="text-lg lg:text-lg xl:text-lg lg:tracking-tight xl:tracking-tighter">
      Say goodbye to inefficiencies and hello to savings with AI-powered automation. By reducing human error and automating processes, your business can cut costs without compromising results. It’s not just about saving money—but maximizing every dollar you invest.
    </p>
    </div>
  </div> 
